
This a Web Application that represents a Hotel System.

It was built using Spring mvc and JSP.

*This app provides services for the users like :

1-Booking a room.

2-Placing Orders(Restaurant or Dry Cleaning).

3-Sending Complaint Messeges.

*This app provides services for the admin like :

1-Viewing all upcoming reservations.

2-Viewing recent orders

3-Adding an Employee Account.

4-Reply to customers complaints.

*This app provides services for the employees(Restaurant or Dry Cleaning ) like :

1-Handle Orders.

2-Adding Items to Menus.

3-Reply to customer Complaints.
